integrity of wound healing, inhibiting the secretion of inflammatory factor and 
tumor necrosis factor and stimulating vascular factor and α-smooth muscle actin 
to the release of vascular growth factor and promote angiogenesis during the 
process of wound healing by immunohistochemical assay.

