Lifelong effect of therapy in young patients with the COL4A5 Alport missense 
variant p.(Gly624Asp): a prospective cohort study.

Boeckhaus J(1), Hoefele J(2), Riedhammer KM(2)(3), Nagel M(4), Beck BB(5), Choi 
