Author information:
(1)Clinic for Nephrology and Rheumatology, University Medical Center Göttingen, 
Göttingen, Germany.
(2)Institute of Human Genetics, School of Medicine, Klinikum rechts der Isar, 
Technical University of Munich, Munich, Germany.
(3)Department of Nephrology, School of Medicine, Klinikum rechts der Isar, 
